data.description: Experience the epitome of comfort and convenience in this fully remodeled & FURNISHED 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, just minutes away from the enchanting Rum Island Park & the breathtaking springs & rivers that define the charm of North Central Florida. This home boasts a stylish metal roof, creating a modern aesthetic & ensuring durability. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of a wood-burning fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for those cool evenings. The property is completely fenced, offering both privacy & security. It's a move-in-ready haven, w/ most of the furniture thoughtfully included, making your transition seamless. Enjoy the convenience of a potting shed, perfect for gardening enthusiasts, & a spacious metal workshop w/ concrete flooring, providing ample space for your projects & hobbies. The master bath features a brand-new step-in shower, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. The property features multiple fruit trees PLUS full RV hook up & no HOA!
